title: 10 Cookbooks 2015 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 latest cookbooks, all in ePUB format:

01. Coconut Oil - Nature's Perfect Ingredient by Lucy Bee (Sep 24, 2015)
02. Cook for Your Life by Ann Ogden Gaffney (Sep 29, 2015)
03. Crack the Code - Cook Any Indian Meal With Confidence by Nandita Godbole (Oct 8, 2015)
04. Serve and Savor: Nourishing Health, Family & Community by Judy Purcell (Oct 11, 2015)
05. Sweets and Treats from Six Sisters' Stuff by Six Sisters' Stuff (Sep 26, 2015)
06. The Big Book of Fabulous Food by Jane Kennedy (Oct 1, 2015)
07. The Dinner Year-Book by Marion Harland (Sep 15, 2015)
08. The Gluten-Free Slow Cooker by Hope Comerford (Oct 1, 2015)
09. The Sailing Kitchen by Lara Reynolds  (Sept 27, 2015)
10. The Supper Club by Phillippa Cheifitz (Oct 1, 2015)
